summary: This is an email chain from January 14, 2021, discussing technical issues with scanned data (SDFL data) for the case US v. Epstein. The issues involve image format mismatches and incomplete image files from a vendor, which need to be corrected to make the data available for review.
keyFacts: The document is an internal email chain regarding the case US v. Epstein.
Technical issues are reported with scanned data from the Southern District of Florida (SDFL), including incorrect image formats and missing files.
A vendor is involved in providing the data, and coordination is needed to fix the issues for legal review.
